headline: Deckers Outdoor Stock: 3 Reasons to Buy and 1 Reason to Sell
summary: Deckers Outdoor is a footwear company with two very strong brands.  Long-term investors need to consider the impact of fashion trends when considering Deckers Outdoor.  Deckers Outdoor (NYSE: DECK) isn't the most descriptive name for the company that owns the Ugg and Hoka shoe brands, among others.
